  "description": "GPU fabric telemetry — NVLink TX/RX bandwidth, PCIe TX/RX, SM and DRAM active utilisation, and NCCL AllReduce latency vs 8 ms RDMA target (from docs/network-design.md). Metrics from DCGM exporter with custom counters CSV (DCGM_FI_PROF_NVLINK_*/PCIE_*/SM_ACTIVE/DRAM_ACTIVE) and nccl-tests probe. TODO(SRE-4): mount custom counters CSV in dcgm-exporter.service.j2 to activate NVLINK/PCIe profiler counters.",
